headline.main: Vintage Western Phone Brands Resurrected by Chinese Players
headline.print_headline: Vintage Western Phone Brands Resurrected by Chinese Players

lead_paragraph: Sevilla moved within two points of La Liga leaders Barcelona with a 1-0 home win over Athletic Bilbao on Thursday, while Atletico Madrid's Fernando Torres was knocked out in a aerial clash at Deportivo La Coruna and taken to hospital.
